      "eligibilityCriteria": {
        "eligibilityDescription_md": "\n  - The applicant must belong to the Socially and Educationally Backward Class (SEBC)/ Economically Backward Class (EBC) or Nomadic Exempted Caste.\n  - The applicant must be a permanent resident of Gujarat.\n  - The applicant must have a total annual family income not exceeding ₹6,00,000/-.\n  - The applicant must have legal ownership of land or a valid allotment order for the construction of a house.\n\n<br>\n\n<br>\n\n",
